            <title>[NIFI-10818] MergeContent 1.17.0 Bin no longer &quot;make room for the new one&quot; as documented</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NIFI-10818</link>
                <project id="12316020" key="NIFI">Apache NiFi</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;MergeContent bin no longer &quot;make room for the new one&quot; This feature works in 1.15.2, but does not work in 1.17.0&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The bug is demostrated in the attached template. The queue before MergeContent will back up do to new bins not being created for correlation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
